				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A PAD spoken by the player character when they finish reading Zanner Toobin's Formula book. The book says: [This book contains a dizzying array of mathematical equations and formulae. Scrawled in the margin, however, is a single line: 'Only Gond's true name can destroy the Neurocitor.']\r\nThe player character reacts based on if they know the Gnomish name of Gond \"Nebelun\"."
				}
